# Esmees first tryout

f %1 THz  %2 THz  %3 GHz    # frequency grid for computation
fout 220 GHz 440 GHz
output f GHz L mm
T0 2.7 K                      # background temperature

layer                        # introduces a layer
P 1014 mbar               # layer pressure of Atacama Desert
T 15 C                       # layer temperature
h 1 km                       # layer thickness
column h2o %4 mm_pwv       # adds a column of h2o to this layer
